      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like there's no point in trying to make it make sense. i keep hoping things will change or that i'll eventually click with people, but i just end up more drained than before. like, even if i stop pretending, i'm still just... here. just existing in this empty space where i don't fit. it feels so much easier to just give up than to keep fighting a battle i've already lost.",
